                              h<ex>an</ex>n</q>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote  scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 2i wrote f. <locus from="109vb:11" to="109vb:17"
                           >109vb:11-17</locus>: <q xml:lang="is">v<ex>er</ex>a</q> to <q
                              xml:lang="is">lítli.</q>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 2j wrote three passages of text: <list>
                              <item>F. <locus from="110rb:15" to="110rb:20">110rb:15-20</locus> fra
