                              </item>
                           </list>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 3 wrote f. <locus from="110va:1" to="110va:11">110va:1-11</locus>
                           from <q xml:lang="is">NV</q> to <q xml:lang="is">oslo</q>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 4 wrote ff. <locus from="110va:11" to="111rb:37"
                              >110va:11-111rb:37</locus> from <q xml:lang="is">Erl<lb/>íngr</q> til
                              <q xml:lang="is">f<ex>oru</ex>
                           </q>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="major" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 5 wrote ff. <locus from="111va" to="120vb">111va-120vb</locus>, even
                           though various minor hands occur here too. In this part of the manuscript
                           the number of lines per column increases from 42 lines per column on f.
                              <locus from="111va" to="111va">111va</locus> to 51 lines per column on
                           f. <locus from="120va" to="120va">120va</locus> 120va (and 50 lines per
                           column on f. <locus from="120vb" to="120vb">120vb</locus>).</p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 5a wrote f. <locus from="116ra:13" to="116ra:26">116ra:13-26</locus>
