                           </q> to <q xml:lang="is">fin<ex>n</ex>a h<ex>ann</ex>
                           </q>
                        </p>
                     </handNote>
                     <handNote scope="minor" script="textualis">
                        <p>Hand 5c wrote f. <locus from="118ra:31" to="118ra:39">118ra:31-39</locus>
